  <fr:p>Suppose we have two centres of contraction <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[a,a':A]]></fr:tex> with <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\chi _\bullet \colon  \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}a = x]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\chi '_\bullet \colon \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}a'=x]]></fr:tex> as witnesses of contraction. To identify 
 <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathopen {}\left \lparen a,\chi _\bullet \right \rparen \mathclose {}]]></fr:tex>
 with 
 <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathopen {}\left \lparen a',\chi '_\bullet \right \rparen \mathclose {}]]></fr:tex>
, we employ the <fr:link
href="foreign-erct-erct-0035.xml"
title="Covariant sum of a left-cloven family of path objects"
addr="//erct/erct-0035"
type="local">covariant sum</fr:link> of each of the <fr:link
href="foreign-erct-erct-001C.xml"
title="Dependent product of path objects"
addr="//erct/erct-001C"
type="local">pointwise path object</fr:link> structures on <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}-=x]]></fr:tex> over the <fr:link
href="foreign-erct-erct-0013.xml"
title="The intrinsic path object on a type"
addr="//erct/erct-0013"
type="local">intrinsic path object</fr:link> structure on <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex>, constructing an identification <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[p\colon  a = a']]></fr:tex> followed by a homotopy <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[H \colon  
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen 
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen \chi _{a'}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
_*^{\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}-=x} \chi _\bullet \right \rparen \mathclose {}
 \sim  \chi '_\bullet ]]></fr:tex>. Fixing <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[z\colon  A]]></fr:tex>, we compute:</fr:p>

  <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[
    \begin {aligned}
      
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen 
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen \chi _{a'}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
_*^{\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}-=x} \chi _\bullet \right \rparen \mathclose {}
 z
      &=
      
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen \chi _{a'}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
_*^{-=z} \chi _z
      \\
      &=
      \chi _{a'}^{-1} \cdot  \chi _z
      \\
      &= \chi '_z
    \end {aligned}
  ]]></fr:tex>

